t;hr data-start=&quot;4940&quot; data-end=&quot;4943&quot; style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;4948&quot; data-end=&quot;5004&quot;&gt;How HRC Service Helps Businesses Save Time and Money&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5006&quot; data-end=&quot;5029&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;In-house HR comes with:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;5030&quot; data-end=&quot;5099&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;5030&quot; data-end=&quot;5042&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5032&quot; data-end=&quot;5042&quot;&gt;Salaries&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;5043&quot; data-end=&quot;5055&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5045&quot; data-end=&quot;5055&quot;&gt;Benefits&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;5056&quot; data-end=&quot;5074&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5058&quot; data-end=&quot;5074&quot;&gt;Training costs&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start=&quot;5075&quot; data-end=&quot;5099&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5077&quot; data-end=&quot;5099&quot;&gt;HR software expenses&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5101&quot; data-end=&quot;5201&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;With &lt;strong data-start=&quot;5106&quot; data-end=&quot;5124&quot;&gt;HR outsourcing&lt;/strong&gt;, businesses pay a predictable monthly fee and gain access to expert support.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5203&quot; data-end=&quot;5300&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Many HRC Service clients reduce HR costs by &lt;strong data-start=&quot;5247&quot; data-end=&quot;5257&quot;&gt;30–50%&lt;/strong&gt; while improving compliance and efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;5302&quot; data-end=&quot;5305&quot; style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;5310&quot; data-end=&quot;5360&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Why HRC Service Outperforms Other HR Providers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-start=&quot;5366&quot; data-end=&quot;5390&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Customized Solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5391&quot; data-end=&quot;5463&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;No one-size-fits-all packages. Every client gets a tailored HR solution.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;5469&quot; data-end=&quot;5503&quot;&gt;Deep U.S. Compliance Knowledge&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5504&quot; data-end=&quot;5557&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;We stay updated on federal and state employment laws.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;5563&quot; data-end=&quot;5589&quot;&gt;Human-Centered Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5590&quot; data-end=&quot;5654&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;Real HR professionals. Fast response times. Clear communication.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;5660&quot; data-end=&quot;5693&quot;&gt;Long-Term Partnership Mindset&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5694&quot; data-end=&quot;5743&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;We grow with your business—not just manage tasks.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;5745&quot; data-end=&quot;5748&quot; style=&quot;font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;h5 style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;5753&quot; data-end=&quot;5792&quot;&gt;Who Should Use HRC Service in 2026?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;5794&quot; data-end=&quot;5819&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: me