(38, 'motivational_speech', '[{\"title\":\"\\u201cWe strive to bring our cutting-edge technology and years of experience to cultivate the ultimate relationship between employer; employee; and technology\\u201d\",\"description\":\"Small business owners \\u2014 is your HR system working for you or against you?\\r\\n\\r\\nHRC HR LMS helps you manage employee training, payroll compliance, and HR documentation all in one powerful platform. Stay audit-ready and protect your business.\\r\\n\\r\\nLearn more today \\ud83d\\udc49 https:\\/\\/lms.hrchr.com\\/\",\"image\":\"HAiT75yjKuvqJ2oEDwcL.png\"}]'),
