elvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Please complete the training by the deadline. If you encounter any issues accessing the link or have any questions, feel free to reach out to Maria Khan, Human Resources at 818-920-6000 X105.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Thank you for your attention to this important matter and for your continued dedication to creating a safe workplace for everyone.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"></li></ol><div style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_signature\" data-smartmail=\"gmail_signature\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: \" comic=\"\" sans=\"\" ms\",=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Sincerely,</span></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms, sans-serif\">Maria Khan</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms, sans-serif\"><br></font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font size=\"1\" face=\"comic sans ms, sans-serif\">VP of Human Resources<br>Hospitality Resource Center (HRC), LLC<br>27703 Zeus Ln<br>Santa Clarita, CA 91351<br>Phone: 818-920-6000<br>Fax: 661-250-8128</font></div><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font size=\"1\" face=\"comic sans ms, sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.hrcservice.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://w