(122, 'marthaaadriana06@gmail.com', 'Mandatory Training By Your Employer & HR', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <title>Mandatory Training By Your Employer & HR</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); text-align: center;\">\n\n    <!-- Logo -->\n    <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n      <img src=\"https://lms.hrchr.com/uploads/system/6e03a3928e2f0af1aacfc88f28e4c94f.png\" alt=\"Website Logo\" width=\"250\" height=\"auto\">\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Email subject -->\n    <h1 style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 25px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Mandatory Training By Your Employer & HR</h1>\n\n    <!-- Email body -->\n    <!-- Start and end hidden div are needed for tracking system notification. SO don\'t remove -->\n    <div class=\"system_notification_start\" style=\"display: none;\"></div>\n    <div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Dear Team Member,</span><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">As part of our commitment to maintaining a safe and respectful workplace, we are requiring all employees to complete a mandatory training. This training is designed to help you recognize and prevent potential workplace violence, ensuring a secure environment for everyone.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"></p><p><b>For mobile app, you can go to Google play store or Apple\'s iOs store and download the HRCHR- LMS App