(6, 3, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span zm=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Segoe UI&#039;;&quot;&gt;Which of the statements about workplace violence is true ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 3, '[\"It is always committed by employees\",\"It may be committed by anyone\",\"It must include physical assault\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
