(40, 23, '&lt;p&gt;Q1. Why is the hospitality industry considered a high-risk environment for human trafficking?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Because hotels are always crowded\",\"B. Because traffickers may misuse hotels for anonymity and control \",\"C. Because staff work long hours\",\"D. Because hotels are open 24\\/7\"]', '[\"2\"]', 1),
(41, 23, '&lt;p&gt;Q2. What should an employee do if they suspect human trafficking?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Confront the suspected trafficker\",\"B. Ignore the situation\",\"C. Follow company reporting procedures and notify management or security \",\"Post about it on social media\"]', '[\"3\"]', 2),
(42, 23, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;&quot;&gt;Q3. Should hospitality employees directly intervene in a suspected trafficking situation?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Yes, always\",\"B. Only if the guest asks for help\",\"C. No, direct intervention should be avoided for safety reasons \",\"D. Only at night\"]', '[\"3\"]', 3),
(43, 23, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;&quot;&gt;Q4. Which of the following is an appropriate action when reporting concerns?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Sharing details with coworkers\",\"B. Maintaining confidentiality and reporting through proper channels \",\"C. Asking the suspected person questions\",\"D. Recording videos secretly\"]', '[\"2\"]', 4),
(44, 23, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;&quot;&gt;Q5. Who should employees typically report concerns to first?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Other guests\",\"B. Hotel management, security, or designated supervisors\",\"C. Social media platforms\",\"D. Friends or family\"]', '[\"2\"]', 5),
(45, 24, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;&quot;&gt;Q6. What is the primary goal of reporting suspected human trafficking?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. To accuse someone\",\"B. To protect victims and ensure safety \",\"C. To collect evidence personally\",\"D. To avoid customer complaints\"]', '[\"2\"]', 1),
(46, 24, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1835&quot; data-end=&quot;1915&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1839&quot; data-end=&quot;1913&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1916&quot; data-end=&quot;2052&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Q7. Why is confidentiality important when reporting suspected trafficking?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. To avoid paperwork\",\"B. To protect privacy and prevent retaliation \",\"C. To keep information secret from management\",\"D. To delay action\"]', '[\"2\"]', 2),
(47, 24, '&lt;p&gt;Q8. Which behavior may indicate a situation worth reporting?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Guests requesting extra towels\",\"B. A guest appearing controlled, fearful, or unable to speak freely \",\"C. Late check-outs\",\"D. Room service requests\"]', '[\"2\"]', 3),
(48, 24, '&lt;p&gt;Q9. What should employees do if they are unsure whether a situation is trafficking-related?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Ignore it\",\"B. Investigate on their own\",\"C. Report concerns to management for review\",\"D. Question the guest directly\"]', '[\"3\"]', 4),
(49, 24, '&lt;p&gt;Q10. What is the safest approach for hospitality employees regarding suspected trafficking?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Take action alone\",\"B. Observe, document if required, and report through proper channels \",\"C. Confront the situation publicly\",\"D. Detain the individuals involved\"]', '[\"2\"]', 5),
(50, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What are blood borne pathogens?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Airborne germs\",\"B. Microorganisms present in blood that can cause disease\",\"C. Harmless bacteria\",\"D. Skin infections\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(51, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Which of the following is a common blood borne disease?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Influenza\",\"B. Hepatitis\",\"C. Asthma\",\"D. COVID-19\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(52, 21, '&lt;p&gt;When should gloves be worn?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only during meetings\",\"B. When handling blood or other potentially infectious materials\",\"C. When typing\",\"D. Never\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(53, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What should you do after a needle-stick injury?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Ignore it\",\"B. Wash the area and report it immediately\",\"C. Continue working\",\"D. Hide the injury\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(54, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What does BBP stand for?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Body Bacteria Protection\",\"B. Blood Borne Pathogens\",\"C. Basic Bio Procedure\",\"D. Blood Based Protection\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(55, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Which organization sets BBP safety standards in the U.S.?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. WHO\",\"B. OSHA\",\"C. FDA\",\"D. CDC\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(56, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Which disease is spread through blood exposure?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Flu\",\"B. Hepatitis C\",\"C. Cold\",\"D. Asthma\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(57, 21, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Blood borne pathogens can enter the body through:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Cuts\",\"B. Eyes\",\"C. Mouth\",\"D. All of the above\"]', '[\"4\"]', 0),
(58, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What is OPIM?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Office Paper Inventory Method\",\"B. Other Potentially Infectious Materials\",\"C. Occupational Policy Instruction Manual\",\"D. Optional Protection Items\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(59, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Which item is considered PPE?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Desk\",\"B. Face shield\",\"C. Pen\",\"D. Notebook\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(60, 21, '&lt;p class=&quot;dropdown-item&quot;&gt;Gloves should be changed when they are:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Clean\",\"B. Torn or contaminated\",\"C. New\",\"D. Expensive\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(61, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Eating or drinking in areas with blood exposure is:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Allowed\",\"B. Encouraged\",\"C. Prohibited\",\"D. Optional\"]', '[\"3\"]', 0),
(62, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What should you do if blood contacts broken skin?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Ignore it\",\"B. Wash immediately and report it\",\"C. Cover with clothing\",\"D. Wait until later\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(63, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Which practice helps prevent BBP exposure?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Recapping needles\",\"B. Handwashing\",\"C. Sharing gloves\",\"D. No PPE\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(64, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Sharps should be disposed of in:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Regular trash\",\"B. Approved sharps containers\",\"C. Plastic bags\",\"D. Cardboard boxes\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(65, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Universal precautions mean:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Treat all blood as potentially infectious\",\"B. Only protect known cases\",\"C. No PPE required\",\"D. Only gloves are needed\"]', '[\"1\"]', 0),
(66, 21, '&lt;p&gt;PPE should be provided by the:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Employee\",\"B. Employer\",\"C. Hospital\",\"D. Government\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(67, 21, '&lt;p&gt;When should BBP training be provided?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only once\",\"B. At hire and annually\",\"C. Every 10 years\",\"D. Never\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(68, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What protects eyes from blood splashes?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Mask\",\"B. Goggles\",\"C. Gloves\",\"D. Shoes\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(69, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What should you do after removing PPE?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Eat\",\"B. Wash hands\",\"C. Touch your face\",\"D. Leave work\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(70, 21, '&lt;p&gt;Which body fluid is NOT considered OPIM?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Blood\",\"B. Semen\",\"C. Sweat\",\"D. Vaginal fluid\"]', '[\"3\"]', 0),
(71, 21, '&lt;p&gt;What is the first step after an exposure incident?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Report the incident immediately\",\"B. Ignore it\",\"C. Go home\",\"D. Finish work\"]', '[\"1\"]', 0),
(72, 21, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Engineering controls are used to:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Increase risk\",\"B. Remove or isolate hazards\",\"C. Replace training\",\"D. Replace PPE\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(73, 21, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Contaminated PPE should be:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Increase paperwork\",\"B. Prevent disease transmission\",\"C. Increase workload\",\"D. Replace doctors\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(74, 20, '&lt;p&gt;What does PPE stand for?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Personal Protection Environment\",\"B. Personal Protective Equipment\",\"C. Professional Protective Elements\",\"D. Primary Protection Equipment\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(75, 20, '&lt;h5 class=&quot;dropdown-item&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;What is the main purpose of PPE?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Increase comfort\",\"B. Protect workers from workplace hazards\",\"C. Replace safety training\",\"D. Improve productivity\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(76, 20, '&lt;p&gt;Who is responsible for providing PPE?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Employee\",\"B. Employer\",\"C. OSHA\",\"D. Government\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(77, 20, '&lt;p&gt;PPE should be used when:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Hazards are eliminated\",\"B. No risk exist\",\"C. Hazards cannot be fully controlled\",\"D. Employees request it\"]', '[\"3\"]', 0),
(78, 20, '&lt;p&gt;Which item is considered PPE?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Chair\",\"\\u2714 B. Safety gloves\",\"C. Desk\",\"D. Pen\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(79, 20, '&lt;p&gt;PPE must be worn:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only sometimes\",\"B. As required by the job and hazard\",\"C. Only during training\",\"D. Only when supervisors are present\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(80, 20, '&lt;p&gt;What protects the eyes from hazards?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Mask\",\"B. Safety goggles\",\"C. Gloves\",\"D. Apron\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(81, 20, '&lt;p&gt;Hard hats protect against:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Noise\",\"B. Head injuries from falling object\",\"C. Chemical exposure\",\"D. Heat\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(82, 20, '&lt;p&gt;When should PPE be inspected?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Never\",\"B. Before each use\",\"C. Once a year\",\"D. After accidents only\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(83, 20, '&lt;p&gt;Damaged PPE should be:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Reused\",\"B. Repaired by employees\",\"C. Replaced immediately\",\"D. Ignored\"]', '[\"3\"]', 0),
(84, 20, '&lt;p&gt;Gloves should be removed:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Anywhere\",\"B. After leaving the work ar\",\"C. At home\",\"D. During work\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(85, 20, '&lt;p&gt;PPE training should include:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. How to wear PPE\",\"B. PPE limitations\",\"C. When to use PPE\",\"\\u2714 D. All of the above\"]', '[\"4\"]', 0),
(86, 20, '&lt;p&gt;Which PPE protects hearing?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Gloves\",\"B. Earplugs or earmuffs\",\"C. Face shield\",\"D. Goggles\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(87, 20, '&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;PPE must fit:&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. One size fits all\",\"B. Properly and comfortably\",\"C. Loosely\",\"D. Tightly\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(88, 20, '&lt;p&gt;When should PPE be cleaned or disposed of?&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. When convenient\",\"B. After contamination or use\",\"C. Once a month\",\"D. Never\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(89, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2500&quot; data-end=&quot;2559&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2504&quot; data-end=&quot;2557&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Which PPE protects against chemical splashes?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2560&quot; data-end=&quot;2628&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2575&quot; data-end=&quot;2578&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2598&quot; data-end=&quot;2601&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2612&quot; data-end=&quot;2615&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Safety shoes\",\" B. Face shield\",\"C. Hard hat\",\"D. Earplugs\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(90, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2635&quot; data-end=&quot;2687&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2639&quot; data-end=&quot;2685&quot;&gt;PPE is the last line of defense after:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2688&quot; data-end=&quot;2783&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2750&quot; data-end=&quot;2753&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2764&quot; data-end=&quot;2767&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Training\",\" B. Engineering and administrative controls\",\"C. Meetings\",\"D. Supervision\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(91, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2790&quot; data-end=&quot;2829&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2794&quot; data-end=&quot;2827&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Employees should use PPE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2830&quot; data-end=&quot;2948&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2852&quot; data-end=&quot;2855&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2902&quot; data-end=&quot;2905&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2927&quot; data-end=&quot;2930&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only if comfortable\",\"B. According to training and instructions\",\"C. Only in emergencies\",\"D. Only outdoors\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(92, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2955&quot; data-end=&quot;2998&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2959&quot; data-end=&quot;2996&quot;&gt;Safety shoes protect against:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2999&quot; data-end=&quot;3088&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3007&quot; data-end=&quot;3010&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3071&quot; data-end=&quot;3074&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Noise\",\"B. Chemical fumes\",\"C. Foot injuries from heavy objects\",\"D. Radiation\"]', '[\"3\"]', 0),
(93, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3095&quot; data-end=&quot;3130&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3099&quot; data-end=&quot;3128&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;PPE should be stored:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3131&quot; data-end=&quot;3220&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3142&quot; data-end=&quot;3145&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3178&quot; data-end=&quot;3181&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3196&quot; data-end=&quot;3199&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. In a clean and dry place\",\"B. On the floor\",\"C. In personal bags\",\"D. Anywhere\"]', '[\"1\"]', 0),
(94, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3227&quot; data-end=&quot;3281&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3231&quot; data-end=&quot;3279&quot;&gt;Respirators are used to protect against:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3282&quot; data-end=&quot;3355&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3290&quot; data-end=&quot;3293&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3332&quot; data-end=&quot;3335&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3343&quot; data-end=&quot;3346&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Cuts\",\"B. Slips\",\"C. Breathing hazardous substances\",\"D. Noise\"]', '[\"3\"]', 0),
(95, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3362&quot; data-end=&quot;3407&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3366&quot; data-end=&quot;3405&quot;&gt;Who must be trained on PPE use?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3408&quot; data-end=&quot;3507&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3424&quot; data-end=&quot;3427&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3469&quot; data-end=&quot;3472&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3483&quot; data-end=&quot;3486&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Managers only\",\"B. All employees required to use PPE\",\"C. Visitors\",\"D. Contractors only\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(96, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3514&quot; data-end=&quot;3555&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3518&quot; data-end=&quot;3553&quot;&gt;PPE should be removed when:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3556&quot; data-end=&quot;3663&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3612&quot; data-end=&quot;3615&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3638&quot; data-end=&quot;3641&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Supervisors leave\",\"B. Work is unfinished\",\"C. Talking to coworkers\",\"D. Leaving the hazard area\"]', '[\"4\"]', 0),
(97, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3670&quot; data-end=&quot;3716&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3674&quot; data-end=&quot;3714&quot;&gt;PPE training should be provided:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3717&quot; data-end=&quot;3809&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3733&quot; data-end=&quot;3736&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. One time only\",\"B. At hire and when changes occur\",\" C. Every ten years\",\" D. Never\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(98, 20, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3816&quot; data-end=&quot;3851&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3820&quot; data-end=&quot;3849&quot;&gt;Why is PPE important?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3852&quot; data-end=&quot;3973&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. It looks professional\",\"B. It prevents injuries and illnesses\",\"C. It replaces safety rules\",\"D. It slows work\"]', '[\"2\"]', 0),
(99, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;296&quot; data-end=&quot;307&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;300&quot; data-end=&quot;307&quot;&gt;Q1.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What is the main purpose of an Emergency Action Plan (EAP)?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Increase productivity\",\"B. Protect employees during emergencies\",\"C. Train managers only\",\"D. Reduce company costs\"]', '[\"2\"]', 1),
(100, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;498&quot; data-end=&quot;509&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;502&quot; data-end=&quot;509&quot;&gt;Q2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Which regulation requires Emergency Action Plans?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;510&quot; data-end=&quot;641&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. OSHA 1910.120\",\"B. OSHA 1910.132\",\"C. OSHA 1926\",\" D. OSHA 29 CFR 1910.38\"]', '[\"4\"]', 2),
(101, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;648&quot; data-end=&quot;659&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;652&quot; data-end=&quot;659&quot;&gt;Q3.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should employees do when a fire alarm sounds?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;660&quot; data-end=&quot;792&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;725&quot; data-end=&quot;728&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;753&quot; data-end=&quot;756&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;773&quot; data-end=&quot;776&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Ignore it\",\"B. Call coworkers\",\"C. Evacuate immediately\",\"D. Finish work\"]', '[\"3\"]', 3),
(102, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;799&quot; data-end=&quot;810&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;803&quot; data-end=&quot;810&quot;&gt;Q4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Which exit should be used during evacuation?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Elevator\",\"B. Nearest safe exit\",\"C. Manager\\u2019s office\",\"D. Main entrance only\"]', '[\"2\"]', 4),
(103, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;949&quot; data-end=&quot;960&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;953&quot; data-end=&quot;960&quot;&gt;Q5.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Why should elevators not be used during a fire?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;961&quot; data-end=&quot;1102&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1022&quot; data-end=&quot;1025&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1083&quot; data-end=&quot;1086&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Too slow\",\" B. Company policy only\",\"C. They may fail or trap people\",\"D. Noise issue\"]', '[\"3\"]', 5),
(104, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1109&quot; data-end=&quot;1120&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1113&quot; data-end=&quot;1120&quot;&gt;Q6.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What is a muster point?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1121&quot; data-end=&quot;1235&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1162&quot; data-end=&quot;1165&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1213&quot; data-end=&quot;1216&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Meeting room\",\"B. Parking space\",\"C. Designated assembly area\",\"D. Reception desk\"]', '[\"3\"]', 6),
(105, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1242&quot; data-end=&quot;1253&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1246&quot; data-end=&quot;1253&quot;&gt;Q7.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Who is responsible for guiding evacuation?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1254&quot; data-end=&quot;1397&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Visitors\",\" B. Any employee\",\"C. Floor Warden\\/Emergency Coordinator\",\"D. Security guard only\"]', '[\"3\"]', 7),
(106, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1404&quot; data-end=&quot;1415&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1408&quot; data-end=&quot;1415&quot;&gt;Q8.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should you do if smoke is present?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1416&quot; data-end=&quot;1535&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1469&quot; data-end=&quot;1472&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1495&quot; data-end=&quot;1498&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1516&quot; data-end=&quot;1519&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Run fast\",\"B. Stay low and crawl\",\"C. Cover eyes only\",\"D. Stop moving\"]', '[\"2\"]', 8),
(107, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1542&quot; data-end=&quot;1553&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1546&quot; data-end=&quot;1553&quot;&gt;Q9.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;When should fire extinguishers be used?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1554&quot; data-end=&quot;1681&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1646&quot; data-end=&quot;1649&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1668&quot; data-end=&quot;1671&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Always\",\"B. Only if trained and fire is small\",\"C. After evacuation\",\"D. Never\"]', '[\"2\"]', 9),
(108, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1688&quot; data-end=&quot;1700&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1692&quot; data-end=&quot;1700&quot;&gt;Q10.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What information should employees know in an EAP?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1701&quot; data-end=&quot;1855&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1771&quot; data-end=&quot;1774&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1829&quot; data-end=&quot;1832&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Marketing strategy\",\"B. Exit routes and procedures\",\"C. Payroll process\",\"D. Office layout only\"]', '[\"2\"]', 10),
(109, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1862&quot; data-end=&quot;1874&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1866&quot; data-end=&quot;1874&quot;&gt;Q11.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should you do after reaching the assembly area?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1875&quot; data-end=&quot;2009&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1989&quot; data-end=&quot;1992&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Leave immediately\",\"B. Wait for headcount\",\" C. Go home\",\"D. Call friends\"]', '[\"2\"]', 11),
(110, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2016&quot; data-end=&quot;2028&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2020&quot; data-end=&quot;2028&quot;&gt;Q12.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What is the correct action if someone is injured during evacuation?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2029&quot; data-end=&quot;2186&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2167&quot; data-end=&quot;2170&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Ignore\",\"B. Report to emergency responders\",\"C. Move them alone\",\"D. Take photos\"]', '[\"2\"]', 12),
(111, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2193&quot; data-end=&quot;2205&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2197&quot; data-end=&quot;2205&quot;&gt;Q13.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;How should employees with disabilities be assisted?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2206&quot; data-end=&quot;2362&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2332&quot; data-end=&quot;2335&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Left behind\",\"B. Carry without training\",\"C. Use elevators\",\"D. Follow assigned assistance plan\"]', '[\"4\"]', 13),
(112, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2369&quot; data-end=&quot;2381&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2373&quot; data-end=&quot;2381&quot;&gt;Q14.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should you do if you discover a fire?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2382&quot; data-end=&quot;2513&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2493&quot; data-end=&quot;2496&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Hide\",\"B. Record video\",\"C. Call manager first\",\"D. Activate alarm and evacuate\"]', '[\"4\"]', 14),
(113, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2520&quot; data-end=&quot;2532&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2524&quot; data-end=&quot;2532&quot;&gt;Q15.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What does “All Clear” mean?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2533&quot; data-end=&quot;2651&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2578&quot; data-end=&quot;2581&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2611&quot; data-end=&quot;2614&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2632&quot; data-end=&quot;2635&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Fire started\",\"B. Shift ended\",\"C. Drill completed\",\"D. Safe to re-enter building\"]', '[\"4\"]', 15),
(114, 25, '&lt;hr data-start=&quot;2653&quot; data-end=&quot;2656&quot;&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2658&quot; data-end=&quot;2670&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2662&quot; data-end=&quot;2670&quot;&gt;Q16.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Why are emergency exit signs important?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2671&quot; data-end=&quot;2804&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2726&quot; data-end=&quot;2729&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2756&quot; data-end=&quot;2759&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2778&quot; data-end=&quot;2781&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Decoration\",\"B. Lighting purpose\",\"C. Guide people to safety\",\"D. Legal display only\"]', '[\"3\"]', 16),
(115, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2811&quot; data-end=&quot;2823&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2815&quot; data-end=&quot;2823&quot;&gt;Q17.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should never be blocked?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2824&quot; data-end=&quot;2928&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;2871&quot; data-end=&quot;2874&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Office desks\",\"B. Emergency exits\",\" C. Windows\",\" D. Storage rooms\"]', '[\"2\"]', 17),
(116, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2935&quot; data-end=&quot;2947&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2939&quot; data-end=&quot;2947&quot;&gt;Q18.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Who should employees report emergencies to?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;2948&quot; data-end=&quot;3087&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3011&quot; data-end=&quot;3014&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3067&quot; data-end=&quot;3070&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Coworkers only\",\"B. Social media\",\" C. Clients\",\"D. Supervisor or emergency coordinator\"]', '[\"2\"]', 18),
(117, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3094&quot; data-end=&quot;3106&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3098&quot; data-end=&quot;3106&quot;&gt;Q19.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;How often should employees be trained on EAP?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3107&quot; data-end=&quot;3246&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3174&quot; data-end=&quot;3177&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3209&quot; data-end=&quot;3212&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3233&quot; data-end=&quot;3236&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Once in lifetime\",\"B. Never\",\"C. Only during drills\",\"D. When hired and periodically\"]', '[\"4\"]', 19),
(118, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3253&quot; data-end=&quot;3265&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3257&quot; data-end=&quot;3265&quot;&gt;Q20.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should you do if you cannot evacuate?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3266&quot; data-end=&quot;3399&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3319&quot; data-end=&quot;3322&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3361&quot; data-end=&quot;3364&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Panic\",\" B. Follow shelter-in-place procedures\",\"C. Hide anywhere\",\" D. Call family\"]', '[\"2\"]', 20),
(119, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3406&quot; data-end=&quot;3418&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3410&quot; data-end=&quot;3418&quot;&gt;Q21.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What is shelter-in-place?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3419&quot; data-end=&quot;3558&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Outdoor meeting\",\"B. Fire response\",\"C. Evacuation drill\",\"D. Staying indoors during certain emergencies\"]', '[\"4\"]', 21),
(120, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3565&quot; data-end=&quot;3577&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3569&quot; data-end=&quot;3577&quot;&gt;Q22.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Why are emergency drills important?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3578&quot; data-end=&quot;3722&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3629&quot; data-end=&quot;3632&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3675&quot; data-end=&quot;3678&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3699&quot; data-end=&quot;3702&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Waste time\",\"B. Prepare employees for real emergencies\",\"C. Impress inspectors\",\"D. Reduce workload\"]', '[\"2\"]', 22),
(121, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3729&quot; data-end=&quot;3741&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3733&quot; data-end=&quot;3741&quot;&gt;Q23.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What should you do with personal belongings during evacuation?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3742&quot; data-end=&quot;3891&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3827&quot; data-end=&quot;3830&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3852&quot; data-end=&quot;3855&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3867&quot; data-end=&quot;3870&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Collect all items\",\"B. Lock desk\",\"C. Leave immediately\",\"D. Carry everything\"]', '[\"3\"]', 23),
(122, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3898&quot; data-end=&quot;3910&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3902&quot; data-end=&quot;3910&quot;&gt;Q24.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;What type of emergencies are covered by EAP?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;3911&quot; data-end=&quot;4055&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;3970&quot; data-end=&quot;3973&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;4011&quot; data-end=&quot;4014&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;4031&quot; data-end=&quot;4034&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only fire\",\"D. IT failures only\",\"C. Payroll errors\",\"D. Fire, natural disasters, violence\"]', '[\"4\"]', 24),
(123, 25, '&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4062&quot; data-end=&quot;4074&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;4066&quot; data-end=&quot;4074&quot;&gt;Q25.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Who must comply with Emergency Action Plans?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p data-start=&quot;4075&quot; data-end=&quot;4197&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;4138&quot; data-end=&quot;4141&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;4159&quot; data-end=&quot;4162&quot;&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;4173&quot; data-end=&quot;4176&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Managers only\",\"B. Visitors\",\"C. All employees\",\"D. Contractors only\"]', '[\"3\"]', 25),
(124, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 0.875rem;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;1. What does HIPAA stand for?&lt;/h2&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Health Insurance Privacy Act\",\"B. Health Information Protection Act\",\"C. Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act\",\"D. Healthcare Information Policy Act\"]', '[\"3\"]', 1),
(125, 26, '&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;544&quot; data-end=&quot;686&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;500&quot; data-end=&quot;543&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 1.5rem;&quot;&gt;2. What is the main purpose of HIPAA?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. To regulate insurance pricing\",\"B. To protect patient health information\",\"C. To manage hospital budgets\",\"D. To control employee records\"]', '[\"2\"]', 2),
(126, 26, '&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;763&quot; data-end=&quot;886&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;710&quot; data-end=&quot;762&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;710&quot; data-end=&quot;762&quot;&gt;3. What is Protected Health Information (PHI)?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only medical diagnoses\",\"B. Health data linked to an identifiable individual\",\"C. Payroll data\",\"D. Insurance premiums\"]', '[\"2\"]', 3),
(127, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;962&quot; data-end=&quot;1036&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;910&quot; data-end=&quot;961&quot;&gt;4. Which rule protects electronic PHI (ePHI)?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Privacy Rule\",\"B. Security Rule\",\"C. Breach Rule\",\"C. Breach Rule\"]', '[\"2\"]', 4),
(128, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;1118&quot; data-end=&quot;1205&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1060&quot; data-end=&quot;1117&quot;&gt;5. Which of the following is a technical safeguard?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Locked filing cabinets\",\"B. Employee training\",\"C. Encryption\",\"D. Security guards\"]', '[\"3\"]', 5),
(129, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;1269&quot; data-end=&quot;1353&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1229&quot; data-end=&quot;1268&quot;&gt;6. Which is a physical safeguard?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Password protection\",\"B. Firewall\",\"C. Locked office doors\",\"C. Locked office doors\"]', '[\"3\"]', 6),
(130, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;1421&quot; data-end=&quot;1509&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1377&quot; data-end=&quot;1420&quot;&gt;7. Administrative safeguards include:&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Security cameras\",\"B. Policies and procedures\",\"C. Software updates\",\"D. Door locks\"]', '[\"2\"]', 7),
(131, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;8. Who must comply with HIPAA?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Only doctors\",\"B. Covered entities and business associates\",\"B. Covered entities and business associates\",\"D. All businesses\"]', '[\"2\"]', 8),
(132, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;1756&quot; data-end=&quot;1850&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1697&quot; data-end=&quot;1755&quot;&gt;9. What should you do if you suspect a HIPAA breach?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Ignore it\",\"B. Delete the information\",\"C. Report it immediately\",\"D. Wait for management\"]', '[\"3\"]', 9),
(133, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;1919&quot; data-end=&quot;2050&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1874&quot; data-end=&quot;1918&quot;&gt;10. Which action is a HIPAA violation?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Encrypting emails\",\"B. Discussing patient information in public\",\"B. Discussing patient information in public\",\"D. Securing paper files\"]', '[\"2\"]', 10),
(134, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;2098&quot; data-end=&quot;2236&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2074&quot; data-end=&quot;2097&quot;&gt;11. What is ePHI?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Employee payroll history\",\"B. Electronic Protected Health Information\",\"C. Encrypted financial records\",\"C. Encrypted financial records\"]', '[\"2\"]', 11),
(135, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;2309&quot; data-end=&quot;2392&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2260&quot; data-end=&quot;2308&quot;&gt;12. How often should HIPAA training occur?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Once\",\"B. Every 5 years\",\"C. Annually or per policy\",\"C. Annually or per policy\"]', '[\"3\"]', 12);
INSERT INTO `question` (`id`, `quiz_id`, `title`, `type`, `number_of_options`, `options`, `correct_answers`, `order`) VALUES
(136, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;2462&quot; data-end=&quot;2587&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2416&quot; data-end=&quot;2461&quot;&gt;13. What is the minimum necessary rule?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Share all data freely\",\"B. Access only the minimum PHI needed\",\"C. Store data indefinitely\",\"D. Remove security features\"]', '[\"2\"]', 13),
(137, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;2658&quot; data-end=&quot;2781&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2611&quot; data-end=&quot;2657&quot;&gt;14. What is required if a breach occurs?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Immediate reporting and investigation\",\"B. Ignoring the issue\",\"C. Deleting records\",\"D. Public disclosure immediately\"]', '[\"1\"]', 14),
(138, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;2844&quot; data-end=&quot;2986&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2805&quot; data-end=&quot;2843&quot;&gt;15. Which is NOT considered PHI?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Patient name with diagnosis\",\"B. Social Security number linked to health data\",\"C. Anonymous health statistics\",\"D. Medical record number\"]', '[\"3\"]', 15),
(139, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;3050&quot; data-end=&quot;3137&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3010&quot; data-end=&quot;3049&quot;&gt;16. What is a Business Associate?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Any employee\",\"B. A third party handling PHI\",\"C. A patient\",\"D. A payroll manager\"]', '[\"2\"]', 16),
(140, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;3393&quot; data-end=&quot;3496&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3339&quot; data-end=&quot;3392&quot;&gt;18. What is an example of secure data handling?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Shared passwords\",\"D. Public Wi-Fi access\",\"C. Strong password policies\",\"D. Public Wi-Fi access\"]', '[\"3\"]', 17),
(141, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;3566&quot; data-end=&quot;3679&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3520&quot; data-end=&quot;3565&quot;&gt;19. What does the Privacy Rule protect?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Financial records only\",\"B. Insurance billing codes\",\"C. Patient health information\",\"D. Employee attendance\"]', '[\"3\"]', 18),
(142, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;3748&quot; data-end=&quot;3826&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3703&quot; data-end=&quot;3747&quot;&gt;20. Which organization enforces HIPAA?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. OSHA\",\"B. IRS\",\"C. HHS (Department of Health and Human Services)\",\"D. CDC\"]', '[\"3\"]', 19),
(143, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;3890&quot; data-end=&quot;4000&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3850&quot; data-end=&quot;3889&quot;&gt;21. What is a breach under HIPAA?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Secure data transfer\",\"B. Unauthorized disclosure of PHI\",\"C. Proper documentation\",\"D. Employee training\"]', '[\"2\"]', 20),
(144, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;4069&quot; data-end=&quot;4185&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4024&quot; data-end=&quot;4068&quot;&gt;22. What is the purpose of encryption?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Increase costs\",\"B. Make data unreadable without authorization\",\"C. Share data publicly\",\"D. Store extra copies\"]', '[\"2\"]', 21),
(145, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;4258&quot; data-end=&quot;4371&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4209&quot; data-end=&quot;4257&quot;&gt;23. What is required for HIPAA compliance?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Policies and regular training\",\"B. Ignoring data security\",\"C. Public access systems\",\"D. Shared credentials\"]', '[\"1\"]', 22),
(146, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;4466&quot; data-end=&quot;4574&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4395&quot; data-end=&quot;4465&quot;&gt;24. What is the purpose of a Business Associate Agreement (BAA)?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Financial reporting\",\"B. Define HIPAA responsibilities\",\"C. Marketing contracts\",\"D. Payroll management\"]', '[\"2\"]', 23),
(147, 26, '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;\r\n&lt;p data-start=&quot;4643&quot; data-end=&quot;4773&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4598&quot; data-end=&quot;4642&quot;&gt;25. Why is HIPAA compliance important?&lt;/h3&gt;', 'multiple_choice', 4, '[\"A. Avoid paperwork\",\"B. Protect patient privacy and reduce legal risk\",\"C. Increase administrative workload\",\"D. Reduce staffing\"]', '[\"2\"]', 24);
